\f2\fs30 \cf3 1\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 After the death of Moses the servant of the\'a0Lord,\'a0the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua\'a0son of Nun, Moses\'92 aide:\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Moses my servant is dead. Now then, you and all these people, get ready to cross the Jordan River\'a0into the land\'a0I am about to give to them\'97to the Israelites.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Moses was asked to do this the first time\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He brought them out of slavery\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They never entered the Promised Land\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We can be Free and Frustrated at the same time.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  The problem is what they saw in front of them\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf3 \super 33\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub We saw the Nephilim\'a0there (the descendants of Anak\'a0come from the Nephilim). We seemed like grasshoppers\'a0in our own eyes, and we looked the same to them.\'94  Numbers 13\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They made assumptions about how they saw them\'85in fact we find out later that the people are terrified of the Israelites because of what God was doing through them.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They saw themselves as less than how God saw them.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a reason you haven\'92t accomplished your \'91If only\'92 yet and many times it is because you have a Grasshopper mentality!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You see yourself as less than God see\'92s you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know about you but I can psych myself out before the battle even begins!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of me starting this church\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nic who meets in a fun center\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have a big enough base\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t\'92 have enough money\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t\'92 know anything about starting a church\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You aren\'92t a good enough leader\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are going to mess this whole thing up\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t know the culture that well and enough people\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are an outsider so no one is going to come to your church\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}YOU ARE A GRASSHOPPER AMONG GIANTS IN THIS TOWN\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The first step in turning your \'91IF only\'92 into a reality is to overcome your grasshopper mentality!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf3 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I will give you every place where you set your foot,\'a0as I promised Moses.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Your territory will extend from the desert to Lebanon,\'a0and from the great river, the Euphrates\'97all the Hittite\'a0country\'97to the Mediterranean Sea in the west.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is a huge area and it is God\'92s gift to them\'85they didn\'92t earn it!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God gives good gifts because He is a good father who loves his children.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God wants to give you good gifts\'85he has put desires in your heart not to make you frustrated but so you would dream bigger and in turn trust Him more!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub No one will be able to stand against you\'a0all the days of your life. As I was with\'a0Moses, so I will be with you; I will never leave you nor forsake\'a0you.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Too often we feel we have messed up and God has taken His promise away from us.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today there are a few people in here who need to start dreaming again for God and realize that you might have missed an opportunity but God isn\'92t done with you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will NEVER forsake you\'85EVER!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For those of you who had HUGE dreams at one point in time and now because of circumstances feel as though God has left you, you need to know He will NEVER leave you\'85EVER!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Be strong\'a0and courageous,\'a0because you will lead these people to inherit the land I swore to their ancestors\'a0to give them.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to stop for a second and point out that almost all of our \'93if only\'92s\'94 affect everyone around us, especially our spouses and family.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And today God may be telling you to do something and it is YOU who will bring your family into a new phase of your life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is you, one person, who God will use to release your family from bondage, to bring about order in your marriage, to break a cycle in your family tree.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it will be tough and cause wars and fights and it will not be easy but God\'92s promise land is always worth it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Be strong and very courageous. Be careful to obey\'a0all the law\'a0my servant Moses\'a0gave you; do not turn from it to the right or to the left,\'a0that you may be successful wherever you go.
\f0\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Keep this Book of the Law\'a0always on your lips;\'a0meditate\'a0on it day and night, so that you may be careful to do everything written in it. Then you will be prosperous and successful.\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 Transition:  In this passage sits something I missed for years:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}3 Ways to see this:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we see as God see\'92s, we will do as God say\'92s\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They are going on a military battle and last time I checked there was nothing in the book of Deut that talked about war strategy.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Without Him we CANNOT, without us He WILL NOT!\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you could do it, it wouldn\'92t be an \'91If only\'92 right?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God will not do FOR you, what He has assigned TO you!\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2
\fs28 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}YOU 
\fs24 or some variation is mentioned 43 times in chapter 1 and 88 in chapters 3-10\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2
\f1\b0\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}18 verses it is 43 times \'96 213 it is 88\'85see the difference?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It always starts with YOU!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are the catalyst in turning your \'93If only\'94 into a reality.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is waiting but He will not do it for you!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Have I not commanded you? \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is God\'92s version of saying \'93We\'92ve already talked about this\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Didn\'92t it come from me?  Didn\'92t I promise you this already?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hey, You can\'92t do this without Me, but I won\'92t do this without you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Be strong and courageous. Do not be afraid;\'a0do not be discouraged,\'a0for the\'a0Lord\'a0your God will be with you wherever you go.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God can give you the assignment, but He won\'92t give you the attitude!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And this is what many of us need to hear this morning.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is telling you today\'85\'94It\'92s you and me\'85that\'92s it maybe\'85but I\'92m all you need!\'94\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You pull the trigger\'85I\'92m with you every step of the way!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Joshua ordered the officers of the people:\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Go through the camp\'a0and tell the people, \'91Get your provisions\'a0ready. Three days\'a0from now you will cross the Jordan\'a0here to go in and take possession\'a0of the land the\'a0Lord\'a0your God is giving you for your own.\'92\'94\

\f0\b\fs18 \super 16\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then they answered Joshua, \'93Whatever you have commanded us we will do, and wherever you send us we will go.\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 17\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Just as we fully obeyed Moses, so we will obey you.\'a0Only may the Lord\'a0your God be with you as he was with Moses.\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 18\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Whoever rebels against your word and does not obey\'a0it, whatever you may command them, will be put to death. Only be strong and courageous!\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
